VerifiedThey met as teenagers in a jazz youth club. Today they’re the award-winning music group @ezracollective (Ezra Collective). 🥁🎷🎸🎺🎹 “It typically starts with a voice note,” says lead drummer Femi describing Ezra Collective’s creative process. “The beauty of being a band is the initial idea is one thing, but we all get our moment to interpret whatever that idea is. I get excited to hear what Joe is going to do to the initial ideas I had, and what James is going to add, and TJ is going to change. And that’s what makes us — that’s what’s exciting about it.” In this edition of The Creative Process, step into the studio as Femi, TJ, Ife, Joe and James bring an all-new improvised track to life and create an original, never-before-heard song. “This moment we’ve just had here, just in this room, it’s been one of my favorite moments playing with the boys in ages. It’s just a lot of gratefulness and joy all mixed together. And I think that’s what people feel when they come to the concerts. The party starts on the stage and everyone is invited.” 🎶💗🎶 Music by @ezracollective3 d
